{
  "name": "read_wechat_article",
  "description": "读取微信公众号文章，自动抓取正文、清洗排版、输出结构化文本",
  "author": "OpenClaw Team",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "category": "web",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "url": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "微信公众号文章 URL，格式如 https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/xxxxxxx",
        "pattern": "^https://mp\.weixin\.qq\.com/s/.*"
      }
    },
    "required": ["url"]
  },
  "returns": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "title": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "文章标题"
      },
      "author": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "文章作者"
      },
      "publish_time": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "文章发布时间"
      },
      "content_markdown": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Markdown格式正文"
      },
      "content_text": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "纯文本格式正文"
      },
      "images": {
        "type": "array",
        "items": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "description": "文章中的图片URL列表"
      },
      "original_url": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "原始文章URL"
      }
    }
  },
  "requirements": [
    "requests>=2.31.0",
    "beautifulsoup4>=4.12.2",
    "markdownify>=0.11.6"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "input": {
        "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ijZyuHyubiX7Dp1tJrxZOw"
      },
      "output": {
        "title": "未来1500天，影视行业的钱会被这1%的人赚走？",
        "author": "郑林",
        "publish_time": "2024-10-12",
        "content_markdown": "未来1500天，影视行业的钱会被这1%的人赚走？\n\n\nOriginal\n\n 郑林\n\n...",
        "content_text": "未来1500天，影视行业的钱会被这1%的人赚走？...",
        "images": [],
        "original_url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ijZyuHyubiX7Dp1tJrxZOw"
      }
    }
  ],
  "notes": [
    "仅支持用户主动提供URL的抓取请求",
    "不允许大规模批量爬取",
    "遵守微信公众平台使用条款",
    "避免高频抓取触发限制"
  ]
}